<item>
            <title>[LU-7418] sanity test_29 failed with  &apos;CURRENT: 7 &gt; 6&apos; </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7418</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity test 29 failed review-zfs-part-1 with &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt; &apos;CURRENT: 7 &amp;gt; 6&apos; 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With logs at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/cb93e408-87c7-11e5-b19e-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/cb93e408-87c7-11e5-b19e-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The test_log contains:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 29: IT_GETATTR regression  ============================== 11:01:22 (1447153282)
first d29
total 1
-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 0 Nov 10 11:01 foo
second d29
total 1
-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 0 Nov 10 11:01 foo
done
 sanity test_29: @@@@@@ FAIL: CURRENT: 7 &amp;gt; 6 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&#8217;s nothing interesting in the dmesg and console logs on all nodes. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is the only failure of this test with this error message this year.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
